  "remarks": "TAi.132 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Consul General, Taliban Consulate General, Peshawar, Pakistan. Afghan passport no. 000737 issued 20 Oct 1996. Member of Taliban Peshawar Military Council as at 2010.  Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Review Pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 21 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended 25 July 2006, 23 April 2007, 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011)",
